Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「相信我吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是书桌小子帮我发现了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉了我「你能听到」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:11:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「我很羡慕啊」
